#df.Date = datetime.strptime(Date, "%d/%m/%Y").strftime('%Y-%m')
from datetime import datetime

train['Date'] = pd.to_datetime(train['Test Date']).dt.strftime('%Y-%m-%d')
train['Year'] = pd.to_datetime(train['Date']).dt.strftime('%Y')
train['Month'] = pd.to_datetime(train['Date']).dt.strftime('%m')
train['Day'] = pd.to_datetime(train['Date']).dt.strftime('%d')

i = int(len(date_y) / 8)
date_y[:i].plot(secondary_y='Frequency', figsize=(20, 5), title='Sensor anamoly with time btw 1958 - 1964')
date_y[i:2*i].plot(secondary_y='Frequency', figsize=(20, 5), title='Sensor anamoly with time btw 1965 - 1971')
date_y[2*i:3*i].plot(secondary_y='Frequency', figsize=(20, 5), title='Sensor anamoly with time btw 1972 - 1979')
date_y[3*i:4*i].plot(secondary_y='Frequency', figsize=(20, 5), title='Sensor anamoly with time btw 1980- 1986')
date_y[4*i:5*i].plot(secondary_y='Frequency', figsize=(20, 5), title='Sensor anamoly with time btw 1987 -1993')
date_y[5*i:6*i].plot(secondary_y='Frequency', figsize=(20, 5), title='Sensor anamoly with time btw 1994 -2000')
date_y[6*i:7*i].plot(secondary_y='Frequency', figsize=(20, 5), title='Sensor anamoly with time btw 2001 - 2008 ')
date_y[7*i:].plot(secondary_y='Frequency', figsize=(20, 5), title='Sensor anamoly with time btw 2008 - 2015')
